<li>It may require general <b><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Cleanup" title="Wikipedia:Cleanup">cleanup</a></b> to meet Wikipedia's <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Manual_of_Style" title="Wikipedia:Manual of Style">quality standards</a>. <small>Tagged since June 2008.</small><br /></li>
</ul>
</div>
</td>
