<li id="cite_note-bill_analysis-23">^ <a href="#cite_ref-bill_analysis_23-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-bill_analysis_23-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="http://info.sen.ca.gov/pub/93-94/bill/asm/ab_1151-1200/ab_1178_cfa_930426_112027_sen_comm" class="external text" title="http://info.sen.ca.gov/pub/93-94/bill/asm/ab_1151-1200/ab_1178_cfa_930426_112027_sen_comm" rel="nofollow">Bill Analysis by Bill Lockyer</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-24"><b><a href="#cite_ref-24" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.redorbit.com/news/health/110415/culture_of_patriarchy_in_law_violence_from_antiquity_to_modernity/index.html" class="external text" title="http://www.redorbit.com/news/health/110415/culture_of_patriarchy_in_law_violence_from_antiquity_to_modernity/index.html" rel="nofollow">Culture of Patriarchy in Law: Violence From Antiquity to Modernity</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-watson-25">^ <a href="#cite_ref-watson_25-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-watson_25-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-watson_25-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="http://www.smartvoter.org/1998jun/ca/or/vote/watson_j/paper1.html" class="external text" title="http://www.smartvoter.org/1998jun/ca/or/vote/watson_j/paper1.html" rel="nofollow">Judge John Watson profile</a></li>
